These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding, soccer, golf
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Sport   | water-polo | snowboarding | soccer | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, skiing, parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | skiing | cycling | sailing | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, bus, scooter
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bus | boat | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, 7up
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | cola | 7up | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, october, september
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Birthday   | september | october | july | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, pomegranate, carrot, cherry
