3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Food   | apple | carrot | pomegranate | cherry |

