.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the lizard##2
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | lizard | hedgehog | rabbit | hamster |

