.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, fuchsia, blue, ebony
1. the person who likes blue is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes fuchsia##2
2. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |
| Color   | fuchsia | blue | ebony | white |

