.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, zombie, spy, fantasy
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |   3   |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy | fantasy | superhero |

 #################################

 
