.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
City: hamburg, boston, hannover, venice
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| City   | hannover | boston | hamburg | venice |

 